name: Losing you
description:
We meet people in our lives with whom we can develop great relationships because of shared interests,  common social circles, or blood connection. But beyond these common reasons are those relationships that are the product of a more spiritual and intimate connection, when two people are bonded on a soul to soul level, they're said to have a soul connection.

Such a connection be it platonic or romantic transcends the practical details that hold together other relationships. It is quite rare to find such relationships but that makes it special.
